text:
There is a (mirroring? versioning?) problem with the documentation on the
website. Enter http://lenya.apache.org/docs/1_4/tutorials/tests.html in your
browser and you will get the page titled 'Writing Tests' along with the
corresponding navigation element. Click on a navigation element, e.g. 'Best
Practises' and the navigation element 'Writing Tests' goes away.
creator: mangst@inventec.ch
mangst@inventec.ch
text:
I feel this has nothing to do with recent version renaming activity; I see this
behaviour for a few days now.

Should be fixed with the next update (approx. 17.07.2007 noon).

If not please open again.

Thanks for the report Markus.
creator: thorsten@apache.org

text: It works. Thanks for fixing, Thorsten.
